# Note: unlike .gitignore, this file intentionally does NOT exclude
# assets/allergen-icons/ or assets/onboarding/icon.webp - EAS Build needs
# these present in the uploaded archive even though they're kept out of the
# public GitHub repo. When .easignore exists, EAS ignores .gitignore
# entirely for upload purposes, so this file must be kept in sync manually.
